abstract: Roger Federer defeats Jarkko Nieminen to reach Istanbul Open tennis tournament quarterfinals; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Federer defeated Jarkko Nieminen to reach the quarterfinals of the inaugural Istanbul Open, where he will play Daniel Gimeno-Traver.

headline.main: Roger Federer Reaches Quarterfinals at Istanbul Open
